**PS-3: Personnel Screening — Operational Status**

**SSP Description (from Day 51):** Background screening for all personnel before OpenMRS access is granted. Third-party screening vendor. HR confirms screening completion to ISSO.

**Implementation Verification:**

HR process review confirmed: all current OpenMRS users are employed staff who underwent background screening as part of the MyClinic onboarding process. HR maintains screening completion records in the HR information system. HR-to-ISSO confirmation process: HR sends a written confirmation to ISSO when a new hire has cleared screening and is approved for system access. ISSO does not create the OpenMRS account until the HR confirmation is received.

Verification spot-check: pulled provisioning records for the five most recently created OpenMRS accounts. Confirmed that each has a corresponding HR clearance confirmation dated before the account creation date. ✓

*Verification Evidence:* HR-to-ISSO confirmation letters for five most recent accounts; account creation dates confirming sequence (HR clearance before account creation).

